BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: CHAD (Chapel Hill & Durham Fun)
UID:event_313673857@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T053041Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T200000
SUMMARY:Free Medieval Combat Training (Durham\, NC) - Broadsword - Armor -
  Rapier
DESCRIPTION:Chapel Hill And Durham Fun with Friends (CHAD) 30s 40s 50s+\nL
 earn the European martial art of broadsword and shield\, wearing steel arm
 or. Or maybe Renaissance dueling with rapier and dagger is more your style
 . Beginners welcome! No experience necessary. Some loaner armor is availab
 le.\n\nRapier instructor: Percival Aldridge\, OD\, OP\nBroadsword instruct
 or: William of Bedford\, KSCA\nAdministrator (KM): Charles Fleming\n*This 
 event is held and managed by the [Canton of Buckston-on-Eno](https://bucks
 ton.windmastershill.org)\, a branch of the* [Society for Creative Anachron
 ism\, Inc.](https://welcome.sca.org/) *and is considered the Official chan
 nel of this group here. Questions regarding its content should be directed
  to [chatelaine@buckston.windmastershill.org](http://chatelaine@buckston.w
 indmastershill.org) or to [socialmedia@sca.org.](http://socialmedia@sca.or
 g.) Inclusion of external links does not indicate implicit nor explicit en
 dorsement of any content or products.*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/chad2015/events/313673857/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260306T235424Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T235424Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
